title: Stop #11 of 2006/2007 PBRJ Tour - Lake Louise, AB, Canada
description: The 11th stop on the 2006/07 North American Peanut Butter and Rail Jam tour went down Saturday, March 24th at Lake Louise Resort. Upon arriving at the hill we found the three custom PBRJ features set up and ready to go. Music by: Riverboat Gamblers.
